titles.title: To reauthorize the Nutria Eradication and Control Act of 2003.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Natural Resources.
Referred to the Subcommittee on Fisheries, Wildlife, and Oceans.

bill.summary:
7/24/2007--Introduced.
Authorizes appropriations to carry out the Nutria Eradication and Control Act of 2003 for FY2009-FY2013.
